<h3 class="stdHeader">Instant two-way mapping communication</h3>
<p>Prefiniti takes mapping to the next level with features that allow the instant sharing of maps and aerial images between you and your customer. With a simple upload from a GPS device, CAD or GIS program, or by using tools embedded within Prefiniti, maps with aerials will be instantly available within the project view. Anyone, including the customer, who has access to a particular project can view the maps and images. No more tedious phone calls, hand-drawn maps, or lengthy on-site meetings with clients to explain complications with terrain. Prefiniti optimizes your communication abilities allowing you to spend more time in the field and less time on the phone. <br /> <img src="/graphics/mapping.jpg" width="550" height="450" /></p>